### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Lista scadenze
GET {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/scadenze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dettaglio scadenza
GET {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/scadenze/{{idScadenza}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crea scadenza
POST {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/scadenze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Bolletta luce",
  "descrizione": "Pagamento utenze",
  "dataScadenza": "2026-06-10",
  "isRicorrente": true,
  "cadenzaGiorni": 30
}

### Modifica scadenza
PUT {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/scadenze/{{idScadenza}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Bolletta luce aggiornata",
  "descrizione": "Pagamento utenze (aggiornata)",
  "dataScadenza": "2026-06-15"
}

### Aggiorna ricorrenza
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/scadenze/{{idScadenza}}/ricorrenza
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isRicorrente": false
}

### Elimina scadenza
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/case/{{idCasa}}/scadenze/{{idScadenza}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

